messages.text: Mom’s making me clean first. Taking a while.
She’s a bitch dude I’m waiting.
You know what I’m not coming anymore.
Do u even know what ur missing out on? This is our first real high school party. U r gonna regret this.
Don’t care. Have fun showing up by yourself. Maybe next time if you can stop being such an ass for once
Hey sam ii am sorry abadout earlier.
Just be careful. Don’t get in anyones car if they’ve been drinking.
Ya dontt worry Rachhel took every1’s keyysad
Alright. We’re cool. I’ll see you tomorrow if you still want to chill.
Yo KElly is hearee. She is saying she wants u to come1!!
She keepsa talkin about ui i think she is in 2 uuu
i am with jaccob he cn come pick u up it isnt 2 late
Who’s jacob? I thought you said Rachel took everyone’s keys
Jacob isnt drinking cuz he’s got to drive home.
Really? Idk if my mom will let me out this late.
Fine can you be here by 12?
Ya I’ll telll jacob. u want us 2 pick u up at the park?
I’m at the park where are you
RUNNING LATE. JACOB WANTED TO PICK UP BEER.
IT ISN’T UP TO ME. IT IS JACOB’S CAR.
Damn okay. Are you still comin?
I’m back in my room. Forget about it.
WAIT COME BACK WE ARE HERE
Okay. I’m coming. What’s with the caps?
I thought you said you were here already?
JACOB HAD TO PICK HIS FRIEND UP JUST CHILL
I’m sorry but you are acting really weird.
JUST CHILL. WE’LL BE THERE SOON.
Joey I am getting tired of this
SORRY CAN YOU COME MEET US? JACOB’S CAR BROKE DOWN
SIDE OF THE ROAD. PINE ISLAND DRIVE AND ATLANTIC
How am I supposed to get there?
Shit okay I’ll go and get my bike
What? Jesus. Where did you hide?
Are you kidding me youre in the sewer? This is just weird. I’m going to call the police.
WE ARE STUCK IN HERE. CAN’T LIFT THE GRATE. NEED HELP.
NO WILL TAKE TOO LONG. RUNNING OUT OF AIR I THINK.
Wait I just realized where is jacob’s car? I don’t see it.
Alright I see it. I’m coming just try and relax.
Alright I lifted it. Looking inside don’t see anything. Where are you?
JACOB PASSED OUT BECAUSE NO AIR. NEED HELP LIFTING HIM UP
Are you kidding me???? We have to call an ambulance.
BY THE TIME IT GETS HERE HE WILL BE DEAD. NEED HELP.
Are you serious you want me to come inside?
Okay. Where are you? Just see a bunch of gross water
I can’t do that without getting in the water. This is insane.
GET IN WATER. YOU ARE MY BEST FRIEND.
TAKE A LEFT WHEN PATH SPLITS
YOU’LL FIND US IF YOU TAKE A RIGHT THEN A LEFT THEN A RIGHT THEN ANOTHER RIGHT
Will text you when I get there. Need to conserve battery.
Stop playing games. Where are you? I need to find you because I can’t remember my way out.
RETRACE YOUR STEPS BY LOOKING AT MY TEXTS
Please tell me you are down here somewhere. Phone is gonna die. Won’t be able to retrace steps.
WHAT I am freaking the hell out
I AM STILL AT RACHEL'S PARTY. NEVER LEFT.
Please help me. I am gonna be lost down here. I can’t contact anyone.
SHOULD HAVE CHARGED YOUR PHONE WHILE YOU WERE CLEANING WITH YOUR MOM
NEVER MAKE ME GO TO A PARTY ALONESam: Joey I’m going to die if you don’t send help.
